&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>Unexplored</span></b><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>: only stars and gas clouds =
visible <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
