</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>Explored, but not currently =
visible</span></b><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>: planets and moons visible,=
 but
ships and bases not visible, displayed with <span class=3DSpellE>gray</span>
hatching<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0=
