</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>Visible</span></b><span lang=
=3DEN-GB
style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>: everything visible<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>I=
n the main
view, when the display is zoomed out to sector or galaxy level, explored
systems have their name displayed next to them. Unexplored systems are unna=
med.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

